        "Siva.Daily.H8.01": "There's a phenomenon on my world where binary stars orbit so closely they share material.$10 I'm beginning to understand the poetry in that image when I'm with you.$4",

        "Siva.Daily.H8.02": "The light around you has a distinct signature.$10 It's become my favorite flavor on this planet.$4 I find myself craving it when you're away.$7",

