        "Siva.Daily.H8.04": "@! My internal resonance frequencies increase when you're near.$4 That's... my species' equivalent of a quickened heartbeat.$10 You have a remarkable effect on me.$7",
        
        "Siva.Daily.H8.05": "Sometimes I wonder what would happen if I couldn't return home.$6 Then I realize that home might be less about a place and more about... being with you.$10 What a strange and wonderful realization.$4",
        
        "Siva.Daily.H8.06": "I told Blik yesterday that you're becoming essential to my happiness.$10 He pretended indifference, but I noticed he left his favorite crystal by your door.$7 He's welcoming you into our family in his own way.$4",
        
